commit.message:
Remove dependency on `base-bytes`

Bytes has been part of the compiler since 4.02, which is also the
minimum required version that dune needs.
Fix the docs for the argument order of FilePath.is_subdir
Add dependency on `seq` for older versions of OCaml
Use `Seq` instead of `Stream` for OCaml 5 compatibility
Document the behaviour of FilePath.get_extension, dirname, and basename.
Update the website, everything is hosted on github now.
Improve documentation and move fileutils to its own directory.
Move benchFind to its own Makefile target.
Remove build marker for 'dune' dependency, see ocaml/opam-repository#14266.
Adapt the release process to dune-release.
